PrecisAmendment (SCHEDULE No. 946) to SCHEDULE B to the FOOD AND DRUGS ACT which adds the "European Pharmacopoeia" to the list of official publications which prescribe standards with which drugs must comply if no other standards are prescribed in these Regulations.
